(**
Alternative
===========
Applicative Functors which also have a monoid structure.
___
Minimal complete definition
---------------------------
 * ``return x``/``result x`` 
 * ``(<*>) f x``
 * ``empty``
 * ``append x y``/``(<|>) x y``
*)
